Package: tidycharts
Type: Package
Title: Create interactive charts using the tidy syntax you know and love!
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Vedha Viyash
Maintainer: Vedha Viyash <vedhaviyash4@gmail.com>
Description: The objective of this package is to allow people to create interactive charts
    using syntax similar to the grammar of graphics. This package is heavily built on top of plotly.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3),
    plotly,
    dplyr
Imports:
    rlang,
    magrittr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2.9000
